443	**Crawl loop integration:**
444	
445	```typescript
446	async crawl(): Promise<CrawlResult | null> {
447	  const collected = await tryCollect();
448	  if (collected) return collected;
449	
450	  const checked = await tryCheckBlocked();
451	  if (checked) return checked;
452	
453	  const ran = await tryRun();
454	  if (ran) return ran;
455	
456	  const spawned = await trySpawn();
457	  if (spawned) return spawned;
458	
459	  return null;
460	},
461	```
